description:
Danny recaps this week's Vanderpump Rules, which was basically an episode of Jax and Brittany Take Kentucky filmed in West Hollywood. Brittany Snow from Netflix's Someone Great also calls in to chat about the new movie, whether there will be a Pitch Perfect 4, plus some of her previous work.


Brittany Snow Interview: 30:32ish
